b'@dmlevitt @laurenthomas Likely the first of many takeovers in the space.  Many REITs trade at huge discounts to private market value- the private market for apartments is very strong (at/near all time highs) while the apartment REITs have languished. 25-50% upside in many of these names $CPT $MAA $ESS'

b'$VNQ $XLRE $KKR $CG - i expect a lot more buyouts in REIT-land. Unsustainable NAV discounts with tons of PE dry powder swirling around and all time low int rates- $CPT and $MAA look especially ripe. https://t.co/ukhqtSFmma'

b'$BPY - buyout offer could be the first of many as private market value is significantly in excess of share price for many REITs.  $MAA $CPT $ESS $EQR $AVB $UDR - all trade at big discounts despite strong private market for apartments. #dividends #reits $BX https://t.co/eg4b4P82fm https://t.co/Ao4Am0wgXu'
